  Showcase events

%p
  We also occasionally deliver engaging showcase events to promote mental wellbeing and encourage people to try new activities that our good for their minds. We've worked with brands like Crussh, Headspace, Positive Touch and even Courvoisier to put together entertaining and rewarding packages that promote wellbeing to the public. We're always looking for imaginative sponsors and clients to create promotional events and start positive conversations about mental and physical wellbeing. 
  
