%p
  Our engagement tools have been tested in situations as diverse as the BBC, Lambeth GP practices, the Secret Garden Party and Brixton Village Market, and we're always looking for new places to test our unique approach. All our engagement tools have been developed in consultation with our academic and NHS partners and have been rigorously tested in a range of social contexts, and are currently being evaluated by the pretigious healthcare research body, Kings Health Partners. All the suggestions we collect are also added anonymously to the Mindapples.org community, and can then be analysed to generate valuable insights and recommendations for decision-makers. So, the more we do, the more you learn. 

